  <title>Start a new game</title>

  <p>To start a new game:</p>
  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Click the <gui style="button">New</gui> button or select
      <guiseq><gui style="menu">Mines</gui>
      <gui style="menuitem">New Game</gui></guiseq> from
      the application menu.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Select your preferred <link xref="board-size">board size</link>.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <note>
  <p>If you are already playing a game, <app>Mines</app> will ask if you want
  to <gui>Start New Game</gui> or <gui>Keep Current Game</gui>. If you choose
  the former, your current game will be lost.</p>
  </note>
